mPAY,is,an,online,payment,platform,that,combines,many,frequently,used,and,innovative,payment,systems,within,one,interface,Available,payment,methods,include,credit,and,debit,cards,national,and,international,online,banking,payments,direct,debit,prepaid,systems,mpass,paybox,PayPal,and,others,mPAY,also,provides,an,intelligent,transaction,management,and,reporting,tool,that,simplifies,the,validation,recording,and,administration,of,all,transactions,processed,through,mPAY,The,entire,system,is,easily,integrated,into,most,online,shops,and,e,commerce,systems,using,the,mPAY,SOAP,API,The,mPAY,website,and,documentation,are,provided,in,English,German,Hungarian,and,Slovak